Description: Python interface to the NIfTI I/O libraries
 The package provides a SWIG'ed interface to the NIfTI and FSLIO
 libraries. Additionally it includes a wrapper class for easy access
 and manipulation of NIfTI files.
 .
 This software is in a very early stage of development!
